thread.title: Chris L.
thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by Chris L.

author: Chris L.
title: Chris L.
text: I have needed three different stamps from Rubber Stamp Champ and each one has been perfect! They made my logo stamp look so good, got the detail just right (a hard thing to do on a rubber stamp). Great prices, great service, fast delivery, what more could want!? I'll never go anywhere else.
